data.description: Welcome to Fayson Lakes! Charm and character abound in this warm and inviting 4 bedroom Cape Cod. Lovely beamed ceilings complement the many modern appointments. Newly finished oak flooring with walnut dowels. Fully updated kitchen with pristine custom cabinetry - down to every dovetail - enhanced by the stainless steel appliances and granite countertops. Completely updated full bath (2019) for two exceptionally sized and updated (2023) downstairs bedrooms with new closets and recessed lighting. Upstairs you'll find two more generous sized bedrooms and with ample closet space -- each sharing a second full bath with a recently reglazed tub! The newly finished lower level is a 'basement in name only' ...from its redone flooring to the pristine sheet rocked and soundproofed walls and ceilings -- including built ins and custom cabinetry, perfect for entertaining!  There's even a second large room, most recently used as a wood shop! The beauty carries outward to the fully-fenced backyard where you can cap off a long day at one of Fayson's lakes by cozying up to your own private fire pit. Conveniently located to shopping, services and major thoroughfares - not to mention Kinnelon's great schools! Hang your hat and grab your fishing pole! Don't hesitate - this beauty won't last!
